# MyTypist — Cline Rules

READ `ai-rules/MASTER.md` BEFORE WRITING ANY UI CODE.

This is the MyTypist project — a Document Operating System for Nigerian users.

## Project
- Stack: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite, raw CSS with CSS variables, Zustand, Motion, Swiper
- Code in: `main/src/`
- Accent: `#6C47FF` | Currency: ₦ only | Mobile-first CSS

## Hard Banned
- Soft gradients, glassmorphism, oversized radii, pill overload
- Generic 3-column equal feature cards
- `Inter` as default font
- Em-dashes (`—`) anywhere
- Pure `#000` or `#fff`
- `window.addEventListener('scroll', ...)` for scroll effects
- Fake product UIs from `<div>` rectangles
- Metric-card grids as dashboard default

## What Good Looks Like — Linear, Raycast, Stripe, GitHub
- Sidebars: 240-260px fixed, solid bg, 1px border-right
- Buttons: 8-10px radius, no gradients
- Cards: 8-12px radius, subtle border, shadow ≤ 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
- Transitions: 100-200ms ease

## Tools
1. `npx shadcn@latest add [component]`
2. `npx shadcn@latest add [21st.dev URL]`
3. `npx shadcn@latest add https://efferd.com/r/[block-name].json`
4. Uiverse.io: fetch link, adapt code

## Installed
- `motion` → `import { motion } from "motion/react"`
- `swiper` → `import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from 'swiper/react'`

## 3D / Spline
STOP. Read `ai-rules/spline-handoff.md`. Write prompt for user. Wait for code.

## Writing
Banned: additionally, align with, crucial, delve, enhance, fostering, highlight (verb), intricate, meticulous, pivotal, showcase, seamless, leverage (verb), utilize, empower, revolutionize, groundbreaking, robust, journey/ecosystem (metaphorical). Default to "is." Short declarative sentences. Full rules: `ai-rules/writing.md`

